ActYukon Quartz Mining Act
Yukon Placer Mining Act
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 9, LITTLE SALMON/CARMACKS FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits, until February 1, 2008, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on lands in the Yukon, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry Order made in 1998.
